review_blob: As a chocoholic, its hard for me to not love this beer. I find it just does everything right, and the color is great. I think it has now surpassed Celebrator as my new favorite.
Always returns to #1 with me after I cant get it for awhile. Excellent in all respects.
Great stout, glad to see one doesnt have to get one from the British Isles for it to have real stout flavor. Good warm or cold, dark and inky, little head action.
Very good Stout, inky color, great with pizza!
My favorite when I visited London. Nothing came close, and my first at, for an American, a warm temperature, and hand pumped. It made me a convert!

beer_brewer_name: Schneider Weisse G. Schneider & Sohn GmbH
